### ========================================
### PROGRAM ENDPOINTS (PUBLIC)
### ========================================

### 1. Get Live Program - MINIMAL (Current) - Solo name y description
# @name getLiveProgramMinimal
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs/live/minimal

### 2. Get Live Program - MINIMAL (Specific Date/Time)
# @name getLiveProgramMinimalAtTime
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs/live/minimal?date=2026-02-14T21:35:00

### 3. Get Live Program - FULL (Current) - Información completa
# @name getLiveProgram
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs/live

### 4. Get Live Program - FULL (Specific Date/Time)
# @name getLiveProgramAtTime
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs/live?date=2026-02-14T21:35:00

### ========================================
### PROGRAM ENDPOINTS (PROTECTED)
### ========================================

### 5. Create Program
# @name createProgram
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rock Clásico",
  "description": "Los mejores éxitos del rock de todos los tiempos"
}

### 6. Get All Programs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get Program by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs/{{programId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Update Program
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs/{{programId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rock Clásico Internacional",
  "description": "Lo mejor del rock clásico internacional"
}

### 9. Update Program - Partial (only name)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs/{{programId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Super Rock"
}

### 10. Update Program - Partial (only description)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs/{{programId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Nueva descripción actualizada"
}

### 11. Delete Program (must not have schedules)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs/{{programId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### ERROR CASES
### ========================================

### Try to create program without name
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Descripción sin nombre"
}

### Try to access without token
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs

### Try to delete program with schedules
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/programs/e84ff159-1e55-4267-8798-8e28300cddd4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Try to access with invalid stationId
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/invalid-station-id/programs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
